<p style="position:absolute;top:1210px;left:856px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft127">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1224px;left:627px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft128">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:46px;left:293px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1210"><b>General Ts &amp;&#160;Cs&#160;Contract</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:46px;left:278px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1210"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:115px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">(E)&#160;Payment&#160;shall&#160;be&#160;made&#160;upon&#160;the&#160;first&#160;request&#160;from&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party,&#160;without&#160;deducting&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:136px;left:176px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">any&#160;commissions,&#160;taxes,&#160;or&#160;expenses&#160;and&#160;without&#160;the&#160;&#160;need&#160;for&#160;&#160;a&#160;judicial&#160;ruling,&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:158px;left:176px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">arbitration&#160;or&#160;otherwise.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:180px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">(F)&#160;The&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;is&#160;entitled&#160;to&#160;confiscate&#160;and&#160;liquidate&#160;the&#160;Performance&#160;Bond&#160;in&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:202px;left:176px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">event&#160;that&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;breaches&#160;its&#160;obligations&#160;under&#160;this&#160;Contract,&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:224px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:246px;left:93px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>3-2&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:246px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>Extension of&#160;the&#160;performance&#160;bond&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:268px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:268px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">The&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;may&#160;request&#160;an&#160;extension&#160;of&#160;the&#160;validity&#160;period&#160;of&#160;the&#160;performance&#160;bond&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:290px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">if&#160;the&#160;reasons&#160;for&#160;this&#160;are&#160;available&#160;in&#160;accordance&#160;with&#160;the&#160;Contract&#160;terms.&#160;The&#160;First&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:312px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1214">Party&#160;shall&#160;send&#160;the&#160;extension&#160;request&#160;to&#160;the&#160;bank&#160;directly.&#160;The&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;shall&#160;bear&#160;<br/>the costs of&#160;extending&#160;the bond.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:356px;left:93px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>3-3&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:356px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>Forfeiture&#160;of&#160;the&#160;performance&#160;bond&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:378px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:378px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">(A)&#160;The&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;has&#160;the right&#160;to&#160;forfeiture of&#160;performance bond&#160;provided&#160;by&#160;Second&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:400px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">Party&#160;based&#160;on&#160;clear&#160;reasons related to&#160;the reasons for&#160;which&#160;the bond&#160;was&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:422px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">provided&#160;according&#160;to&#160;Contract&#160;terms&#160;and&#160;conditions&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:444px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:444px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">(B)&#160;The&#160;request&#160;for&#160;forfeiture shall&#160;be addressed&#160;directly&#160;and&#160;explicitly&#160;to&#160;the bank,&#160;and&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:466px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">the bank shall&#160;respond&#160;to&#160;the&#160;request&#160;immediately&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:488px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:488px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">(C)&#160;The&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;may&#160;forfeit&#160;the&#160;performance&#160;bond&#160;of&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;in&#160;the event&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:510px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">that&#160;it&#160;breaches&#160;its&#160;obligations under&#160;this&#160;Contract.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:532px;left:101px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>4&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:532px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>Financial&#160;consideration and&#160;payment&#160;mechanism&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:554px;left:93px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>4-1&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:554px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>Terms&#160;of&#160;payment&#160;of&#160;the&#160;financial consideration&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:576px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:576px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>(A)</b>The&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;pays&#160;the value of&#160;the&#160;Contract&#160;to&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;according&#160;to&#160;what&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:598px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">is&#160;stipulated in&#160;Appendix&#160;(8)</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:597px;left:381px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">&#160;(Drawings&#160;and&#160;Bill&#160;of&#160;Quantities&#160;&amp;&#160;Financial&#160;values)&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:620px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1214">and&#160;after&#160;deducting&#160;what&#160;is imposed&#160;on&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;in&#160;terms&#160;of&#160;fines,&#160;<br/>penalties,&#160;or&#160;other&#160;deductions&#160;under&#160;the provisions of&#160;this&#160;Contract.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:664px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:664px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">(B)&#160;The&#160;representative of&#160;the First&#160;Party&#160;reviews each&#160;invoice submitted to&#160;it&#160;by&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:686px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">Second&#160;Party&#160;and&#160;ensures&#160;that&#160;it&#160;confirms&#160;the specifications and&#160;quantities&#160;agreed&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:708px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">upon&#160;under&#160;the Contract.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:730px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:730px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>(C)&#160;</b>The&#160;amounts due&#160;are paid&#160;according&#160;to&#160;an&#160;invoice submitted by&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:752px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">to&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;within&#160;sixty&#160;(60)&#160;days&#160;from&#160;the&#160;date of&#160;the First&#160;Party&#160;’s approval&#160;of&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:774px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">the invoice after&#160;verifying&#160;that&#160;it&#160;meets all&#160;the legal&#160;justifications for&#160;payment.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:796px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:796px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>(D)&#160;</b>The&#160;amounts paid&#160;to&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;shall&#160;not&#160;exceed the value of&#160;the Works&#160;that&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:818px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">have been&#160;completed,&#160;and&#160;the amounts&#160;paid&#160;to&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;in&#160;the last&#160;invoice&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:840px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">before final&#160;invoice shall&#160;not&#160;exceed 90%&#160;of&#160;the&#160;total&#160;value&#160;of&#160;the Contract&#160;if&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:862px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">applicable if&#160;there is&#160;a&#160;performance&#160;guarantee.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:884px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:884px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>(E)&#160;</b>The&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;shall&#160;submit&#160;monthly&#160;payment&#160;applications&#160;regardless&#160;of&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:906px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">progress&#160;achieved&#160;if applicable.&#160;&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:928px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:928px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>(F)&#160;</b>The&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;has&#160;the right&#160;to&#160;make&#160;any&#160;&#160;corrections&#160;or&#160;amendments to&#160;any&#160;interim&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:950px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">invoice of&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;as&#160;a&#160;result&#160;of&#160;any&#160;errors&#160;that&#160;occurred in&#160;previous&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:972px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">invoices&#160;that&#160;were approved or&#160;paid&#160;to&#160;the second&#160;party.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:994px;left:93px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>4-2&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:994px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>Advance&#160;payment&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1016px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1212"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1016px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1211">(A)&#160;The&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;may&#160;disburse&#160;an&#160;advance&#160;payment&#160;to&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;as&#160;shown&#160;in&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1038px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1215">(Contract&#160;data),&#160;in&#160;return&#160;for&#160;a&#160;bank&#160;guarantee&#160;issued&#160;by&#160;Saudi&#160;Bank&#160;ONLY&#160;of&#160;the&#160;<br/>same&#160;amount&#160;as&#160;the&#160;advance&#160;payment,&#160;provided&#160;that&#160;the&#160;bank&#160;guarantee&#160;shall&#160;be&#160;</p>
</div>
