<p style="position:absolute;top:46px;left:293px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1810"><b>General Ts &amp;&#160;Cs&#160;Contract</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:46px;left:278px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1810"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:115px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">without&#160;prejudice&#160;to&#160;the&#160;right&#160;of&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;to&#160;claim&#160;its&#160;dues&#160;up&#160;to&#160;the&#160;date&#160;of&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:136px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">termination&#160;for&#160;the service provided&#160;and&#160;agreed&#160;by&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:158px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:158px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">(B)&#160;The&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;may,&#160;at&#160;its&#160;discretion,&#160;terminate&#160;the&#160;Contract&#160;or&#160;withdraw&#160;the&#160;Works&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:180px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">from&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party.&#160;The&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;may&#160;execute&#160;the&#160;remainder&#160;of&#160;the&#160;Works&#160;at&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:202px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">the&#160;&#160;Second&#160;&#160;Party’s&#160;&#160;expense&#160;&#160;and&#160;&#160;may&#160;&#160;also&#160;&#160;confiscate&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;Performance&#160;&#160;Bond,&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:224px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">without&#160;prejudice&#160;to&#160;its&#160;right&#160;to&#160;claim&#160;additional&#160;compensation&#160;for&#160;any&#160;damages,&#160;in&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:246px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">any&#160;of&#160;the following&#160;cases:&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:268px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:268px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;&#160;1.&#160;If&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;materially&#160;fails&#160;to&#160;perform&#160;the&#160;Works&#160;in&#160;accordance&#160;with&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:290px;left:174px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">terms&#160;of&#160;the&#160;Contract,&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party’s&#160;requirements,&#160;or&#160;issued&#160;instructions,&#160;or&#160;if&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:312px;left:174px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1814">the&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;delays&#160;implementation&#160;to&#160;an&#160;extent&#160;that&#160;completion&#160;within&#160;the&#160;<br/>agreed&#160;timeframe&#160;is&#160;deemed&#160;unlikely&#160;by&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party.&#160;In&#160;such&#160;cases,&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:356px;left:174px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">shall&#160;provide&#160;&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;with&#160;a&#160;&#160;written&#160;warning&#160;of&#160;fifteen&#160;&#160;(15)&#160;days&#160;before&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:378px;left:174px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">termination.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:400px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:400px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;&#160;2.&#160;&#160;If&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;Second&#160;&#160;Party,&#160;&#160;directly&#160;&#160;or&#160;&#160;indirectly,&#160;&#160;through&#160;&#160;itself&#160;&#160;or&#160;&#160;others,&#160;&#160;has&#160;&#160;offered,&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:422px;left:174px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">given,&#160;or&#160;promised&#160;money&#160;or&#160;any&#160;other&#160;benefit&#160;to&#160;obtain&#160;this&#160;Contract.&#160;Such&#160;actions&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:444px;left:174px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">shall&#160;not&#160;exempt&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;from&#160;potential&#160;criminal&#160;liability.&#160;If&#160;this&#160;occurs,&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:466px;left:174px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">the&#160;&#160;First&#160;&#160;Party&#160;&#160;shall&#160;&#160;also&#160;&#160;have&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;right&#160;&#160;to&#160;&#160;terminate&#160;&#160;any&#160;&#160;other&#160;&#160;agreements&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:488px;left:174px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">concluded with&#160;the Second&#160;Party.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:510px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:510px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;&#160;3.&#160;&#160;If&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;Second&#160;&#160;Party&#160;&#160;becomes&#160;&#160;bankrupt,&#160;&#160;enters&#160;&#160;into&#160;&#160;composition&#160;&#160;with&#160;&#160;creditors,&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:532px;left:174px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">makes&#160;&#160;an&#160;&#160;assignment&#160;&#160;for&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;benefit&#160;&#160;of&#160;&#160;creditors,&#160;&#160;goes&#160;&#160;into&#160;&#160;liquidation,&#160;&#160;has&#160;&#160;a&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:554px;left:174px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1815">receiver&#160;appointed,&#160;or&#160;undergoes&#160;any&#160;similar&#160;procedure&#160;that&#160;adversely&#160;affects&#160;the&#160;<br/>execution&#160;of&#160;the&#160;Works.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:598px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:598px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;&#160;4.&#160;If&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;abandons&#160;the Contract&#160;or&#160;engages&#160;a&#160;Subcontractor&#160;to&#160;execute&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:620px;left:174px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">the Works&#160;without&#160;obtaining&#160;the prior&#160;written&#160;consent&#160;of&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:648px;left:93px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1812"><b>7-3&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:648px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1812"><b>Termination of&#160;the&#160;Contract&#160;due&#160;to&#160;force&#160;majeure&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:670px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:670px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">(A)&#160;The&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;may&#160;terminate the&#160;Contract&#160;due to&#160;force majeure by&#160;virtue&#160;of&#160;a&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:692px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">written notice sent&#160;to&#160;the Second&#160;Party,&#160;in&#160;the following&#160;two&#160;cases:&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:714px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:714px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;&#160;1.&#160;If&#160;the force majeure prevents&#160;the First&#160;Party&#160;from&#160;carrying&#160;out&#160;any&#160;of&#160;its&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:736px;left:174px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">obligations under&#160;the Contract&#160;and&#160;the&#160;force majeure continues&#160;for&#160;more than&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:758px;left:174px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">sixty&#160;(60)&#160;days.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:780px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:780px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;&#160;2.&#160;If&#160;the force majeure prevents&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;from&#160;carrying&#160;out&#160;the&#160;services&#160;and&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:802px;left:174px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">any&#160;of&#160;its obligations&#160;under&#160;this&#160;Contract&#160;for&#160;a&#160;period&#160;of&#160;more than&#160;sixty&#160;(60)&#160;days.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:824px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:824px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">(B)&#160;In&#160;the event&#160;of&#160;termination&#160;of&#160;this&#160;Contract&#160;due to&#160;force majeure in&#160;accordance&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:846px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">with&#160;the provisions of&#160;paragraph&#160;(A)&#160;of&#160;this&#160;clause,&#160;this&#160;Contract&#160;shall&#160;be&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:868px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">considered terminated&#160;within&#160;the period&#160;indicated in&#160;the&#160;termination&#160;notice.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:890px;left:93px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1812"><b>7-4&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:890px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1812"><b>Obligations&#160;of&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;upon termination of&#160;the&#160;Contract&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:912px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:912px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">In&#160;the&#160;event&#160;that&#160;the&#160;Contract&#160;is&#160;terminated&#160;in&#160;accordance&#160;with&#160;the&#160;provisions&#160;of&#160;this&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:934px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">clause&#160;(7)&#160;(Contract&#160;duration&#160;and&#160;termination),&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;shall&#160;do&#160;the&#160;following:&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:956px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:956px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">(A)&#160;Cease and&#160;stop&#160;executing&#160;Works&#160;unless&#160;instructions&#160;have been&#160;issued&#160;in this&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:978px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">regard&#160;by&#160;the representative of&#160;the First&#160;Party&#160;to&#160;protect&#160;people or&#160;property&#160;or&#160;to&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1000px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">ensure the safety&#160;of&#160;the executed&#160;Works.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1022px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1022px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">(B)&#160;Hand&#160;over&#160;all&#160;Contract&#160;documents,&#160;mechanical&#160;supplies,&#160;materials,&#160;and&#160;other&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1044px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">Works&#160;on&#160;the site to&#160;the First&#160;Party,&#160;which&#160;are owned&#160;by&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1066px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1066px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1811">(C)&#160;Remove all&#160;other&#160;supplies&#160;from&#160;the site except&#160;for&#160;safety&#160;reasons.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1088px;left:93px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1812"><b>7-5</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1086px;left:118px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1812"><b>&#160;&#160;Settlement&#160;with the&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;in cases&#160;of&#160;Contract&#160;termination&#160;</b></p>
</div>
</body>
