<p style="position:absolute;top:1210px;left:856px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft197">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1224px;left:627px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft198">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:46px;left:293px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1910"><b>General Ts &amp;&#160;Cs&#160;Contract</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:46px;left:278px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1910"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:115px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:115px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">In&#160;the&#160;event&#160;that&#160;the&#160;Contract&#160;is&#160;terminated&#160;by&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;in&#160;accordance&#160;with&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:136px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">provisions&#160;of&#160;clause&#160;(7-2)&#160;(Termination&#160;of&#160;the&#160;Contract&#160;by&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party),&#160;clause&#160;(7-3)&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:158px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">(Termination&#160;of&#160;the&#160;Contract&#160;due&#160;to&#160;force&#160;majeure),&#160;then&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;shall,&#160;after&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:180px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">notice of&#160;termination&#160;of&#160;the Contract&#160;becomes&#160;effective,&#160;do&#160;the following:&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:202px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:202px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">(A)&#160;Pay&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;for&#160;the&#160;accepted&#160;Works&#160;that&#160;have&#160;been&#160;implemented&#160;and&#160;their&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:224px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">conformity&#160;&#160;with&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;specifications&#160;&#160;contained&#160;&#160;in&#160;&#160;this&#160;&#160;Contract&#160;&#160;was&#160;&#160;verified,&#160;&#160;in&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:246px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">addition&#160;to&#160;the&#160;supplies&#160;and&#160;materials&#160;on&#160;the&#160;Site&#160;which&#160;are&#160;in&#160;good&#160;condition&#160;and&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:268px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">were approved&#160;by&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;before the&#160;date of&#160;notification&#160;of&#160;termination&#160;of&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:290px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">Contract&#160;&#160;and&#160;&#160;recovering&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;remaining&#160;&#160;balance&#160;&#160;from&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;value&#160;&#160;of&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;Advance&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:312px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">Payment&#160;(if&#160;any).&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:334px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:334px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">(B)&#160;Release&#160;the&#160;Advance&#160;Payment&#160;guarantee&#160;and&#160;performance&#160;bond,&#160;after&#160;making&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:356px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">necessary&#160;settlements,&#160;unless&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;confiscated&#160;the&#160;performance&#160;bond&#160;in&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:378px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">reference to&#160;clause (7-2)&#160;paragraph&#160;(B).&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:400px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:400px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">(C)&#160;&#160;If&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;First&#160;&#160;Party&#160;&#160;terminates&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;Contract&#160;&#160;based&#160;&#160;on&#160;&#160;a&#160;&#160;recommendation&#160;&#160;from&#160;&#160;its&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:422px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">competent&#160;&#160;committee,&#160;&#160;it&#160;&#160;is&#160;&#160;permissible&#160;&#160;for&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;First&#160;&#160;Party&#160;&#160;to&#160;&#160;take&#160;&#160;whatever&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:444px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">measures&#160;it&#160;deems&#160;appropriate&#160;to&#160;preserve&#160;its&#160;rights,&#160;such&#160;as&#160;seizing&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:466px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">Party’s&#160;&#160;entitlements&#160;&#160;until&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;final&#160;&#160;accounting&#160;&#160;is&#160;&#160;conducted,&#160;&#160;or&#160;&#160;to&#160;&#160;suspend&#160;&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:488px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">decision&#160;to&#160;terminate&#160;the&#160;Contract&#160;and&#160;continue&#160;to&#160;manage the&#160;Contract&#160;work&#160;itself&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:510px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">or&#160;through&#160;another&#160;contractor&#160;&#160;at&#160;the&#160;expense&#160;of&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party,&#160;if&#160;he&#160;believes&#160;that&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:532px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">there is&#160;an&#160;benefit&#160;for&#160;the project&#160;in its&#160;continuation.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:554px;left:93px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1912"><b>7-6&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:554px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1912"><b>General&#160;provisions&#160;on termination&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:576px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:576px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">(A)&#160;These&#160;termination&#160;provisions&#160;provide&#160;exclusively&#160;for&#160;the&#160;cases&#160;in&#160;which&#160;the&#160;Contract&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:598px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">may&#160;be&#160;terminated.&#160;The&#160;party&#160;who&#160;deems&#160;that&#160;he&#160;is&#160;harmed&#160;by&#160;the&#160;breach&#160;of&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:620px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1914">other&#160;&#160;party&#160;&#160;-&#160;&#160;at&#160;&#160;his&#160;&#160;absolute&#160;&#160;discretion&#160;&#160;-&#160;&#160;has&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;right&#160;&#160;to&#160;&#160;refer&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;dispute&#160;&#160;in&#160;<br/>accordance&#160;&#160;with&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;provisions&#160;&#160;of&#160;&#160;Article&#160;&#160;(5)&#160;&#160;(Applicable&#160;&#160;Law&#160;&#160;and&#160;&#160;Dispute&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:664px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">Resolution)&#160;of&#160;the&#160;main&#160;Contract&#160;agreement&#160;to&#160;protect&#160;his&#160;interests&#160;lawful&#160;and&#160;for&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:686px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">any&#160;&#160;compensation&#160;&#160;he&#160;&#160;may&#160;&#160;be&#160;&#160;entitled&#160;&#160;to&#160;&#160;for&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;breach&#160;&#160;(including&#160;&#160;reasonable&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:708px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">expenses&#160;and&#160;costs incurred in&#160;doing&#160;so).&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:730px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:730px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">(B)&#160;Termination&#160;of&#160;the&#160;Contract&#160;does&#160;not&#160;affect&#160;any&#160;rights&#160;or&#160;obligations&#160;of&#160;the&#160;parties&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:752px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">prior&#160;to&#160;the date of&#160;termination.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:774px;left:93px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1912"><b>7-7&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:774px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1912"><b>Suspension of&#160;work&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:796px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:796px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">(A)&#160;(A)&#160;The First&#160;Party&#160;shall&#160;have the&#160;right&#160;to&#160;suspend&#160;the execution&#160;of&#160;the Works,&#160;in&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:818px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">whole or&#160;in&#160;part, by&#160;providing&#160;written&#160;notice&#160;to&#160;the Second&#160;Party.&#160;The notice shall&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:840px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">specify&#160;the commencement&#160;date of&#160;the suspension&#160;and,&#160;when applicable,&#160;the date&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:862px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">of&#160;resumption&#160;once&#160;the&#160;reasons for&#160;suspension&#160;have ceased.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:884px;left:163px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">1.&#160;&#160;If&#160;the Works&#160;are fully&#160;suspended,&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;shall&#160;be granted an&#160;extension&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:906px;left:190px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">of&#160;time equivalent&#160;to&#160;the full&#160;suspension&#160;period.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:928px;left:163px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">2.&#160;&#160;If&#160;the suspension&#160;is&#160;partial,&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;shall&#160;be granted an&#160;extension&#160;of&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:950px;left:190px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">time proportionate to&#160;the impact&#160;of&#160;the suspended Works&#160;on&#160;the progress&#160;of&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:972px;left:190px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">Project. Such&#160;an&#160;extension&#160;shall&#160;be based on&#160;a&#160;formal&#160;request&#160;for&#160;an&#160;extension&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:994px;left:190px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">of&#160;time submitted by&#160;the Second&#160;Party.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1016px;left:163px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">3.&#160;&#160;For&#160;every&#160;thirty&#160;(30)&#160;consecutive days&#160;of&#160;total&#160;suspension, the Second&#160;Party&#160;shall&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1038px;left:190px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1915">be&#160;entitled&#160;to&#160;three&#160;(3)&#160;additional&#160;days&#160;for&#160;mobilization&#160;and&#160;preparation&#160;to&#160;resume&#160;<br/>the&#160;&#160;Works.&#160;&#160;However,&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;total&#160;&#160;additional&#160;&#160;mobilization&#160;&#160;period&#160;&#160;shall&#160;&#160;not&#160;&#160;exceed&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1081px;left:190px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft1911">forty-five (45)&#160;days.&#160;</p>
