<p style="position:absolute;top:1213px;left:710px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft257">&#160;.ةيدوعسلا&#160;ةيبرعلا&#160;ةكلمملا</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1210px;left:856px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft257">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1224px;left:627px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft258">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:46px;left:293px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2510"><b>General Ts &amp;&#160;Cs&#160;Contract</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:46px;left:278px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2510"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:115px;left:88px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2511"><b>11-4&#160;&#160;Existing Site&#160;conditions&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:136px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:136px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">The&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;acknowledges&#160;that&#160;it&#160;has&#160;completed and&#160;studied&#160;all&#160;the information&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:158px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">before submitting&#160;its&#160;offers&#160;and&#160;that&#160;the prices&#160;included in&#160;its offers are&#160;sufficient&#160;to&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:180px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">cover&#160;all&#160;its obligations&#160;under&#160;the Contract&#160;and&#160;other&#160;matters&#160;necessary&#160;to&#160;complete&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:202px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">and&#160;carry&#160;out&#160;the work in a&#160;perfect&#160;and&#160;proper&#160;manner.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:224px;left:88px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2511"><b>11-5&#160;&#160;Unforeseen Site&#160;Conditions&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:246px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:246px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">(A)&#160;If&#160;during&#160;the&#160;implementation&#160;of&#160;the&#160;Works,&#160;one&#160;of&#160;the&#160;hidden&#160;defects&#160;appeared&#160;in&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:268px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">the Site that&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;or&#160;an&#160;expert&#160;was&#160;not&#160;able to&#160;identify,&#160;then&#160;the Second&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:290px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">Party&#160;shall,&#160;within&#160;a&#160;period&#160;of&#160;(10)&#160;ten&#160;days&#160;from&#160;the&#160;date&#160;of&#160;the&#160;appearance&#160;of&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:312px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2515">hidden&#160;&#160;defects,&#160;&#160;notify&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;representative&#160;&#160;of&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;First&#160;&#160;Party&#160;&#160;of&#160;&#160;those&#160;&#160;defects.&#160;&#160;The&#160;<br/>Second&#160;Party,&#160;when&#160;requested&#160;to&#160;do&#160;so,&#160;shall&#160;prepare&#160;a&#160;report&#160;to&#160;be&#160;submitted&#160;to&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:356px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">representative&#160;of&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party,&#160;specifying&#160;precisely&#160;the&#160;defects&#160;that&#160;occurred&#160;in&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:378px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">Site&#160;or&#160;in&#160;the&#160;neighboring&#160;areas,&#160;provided&#160;that&#160;this&#160;report&#160;includes&#160;the&#160;proposals&#160;of&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:400px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">the&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;to&#160;overcome&#160;the&#160;apparent&#160;defects,&#160;the&#160;time&#160;required&#160;to&#160;resume&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:422px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">work,&#160;and&#160;the estimated&#160;resulting&#160;additional&#160;Cost&#160;details (if any).&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:444px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:444px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">(B)&#160;The&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;is&#160;not&#160;responsible&#160;for&#160;any&#160;additional&#160;costs&#160;claimed&#160;by&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:466px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">Party&#160;if&#160;it&#160;fails&#160;to&#160;notify&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;during&#160;the&#160;notification&#160;period&#160;mentioned&#160;in&#160;this&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:488px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">clause.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:510px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:510px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">(C)&#160;The&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;shall,&#160;in&#160;the&#160;event&#160;of&#160;the&#160;emergence&#160;of&#160;a&#160;hidden&#160;defect,&#160;do&#160;its&#160;best&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:532px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">to&#160;prevent&#160;or&#160;reduce the losses&#160;resulting&#160;from&#160;it&#160;as&#160;much&#160;as&#160;possible.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:554px;left:88px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2511"><b>11-6&#160;&#160;Inspection of&#160;Adjacent&#160;Property</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:554px;left:402px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2513"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:554px;left:406px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">–&#160;If&#160;applicable<b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:576px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:576px;left:141px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">(A)&#160;The&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;shall, before commencing&#160;the implementation&#160;of&#160;any&#160;demolition,&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:598px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">backfilling,&#160;consolidation,&#160;concrete stabilization, or&#160;any&#160;of&#160;the Works&#160;specified&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:620px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2515">under&#160;this&#160;Contract, inspect&#160;the property&#160;adjacent&#160;to&#160;the site and&#160;the tools&#160;and&#160;<br/>equipment&#160;therein.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:664px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:664px;left:141px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">(B)&#160;The neighboring&#160;property&#160;is&#160;inspected&#160;in the&#160;presence of&#160;the owner&#160;or&#160;its&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:686px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">representative whenever&#160;possible,&#160;and&#160;the inspection&#160;is&#160;carried&#160;out&#160;by&#160;all&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:708px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">appropriate means&#160;to&#160;determine&#160;the&#160;exact&#160;condition&#160;of&#160;the neighboring&#160;property&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:730px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">before starting&#160;work.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:752px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:752px;left:141px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">(C)&#160;Prior&#160;notice&#160;of&#160;such&#160;inspection&#160;shall&#160;be given to&#160;the First&#160;Party&#160;and&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:774px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">representative of&#160;the First&#160;Party&#160;may&#160;attend&#160;the&#160;inspection&#160;upon&#160;his&#160;request, and&#160;a&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:796px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2515">copy&#160;of&#160;the documents and&#160;the inspection&#160;report&#160;that&#160;took place after&#160;being&#160;signed&#160;<br/>by&#160;the owner&#160;of&#160;the adjacent&#160;plot&#160;must&#160;be submitted to&#160;the representative of&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:840px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">First&#160;Party,&#160;and&#160;this&#160;shall&#160;be done with&#160;each&#160;plot&#160;separately.&#160;The inspection,&#160;once&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:862px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">conducted,&#160;is not&#160;considered&#160;one of&#160;the reasons&#160;for&#160;exempting&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:884px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">from&#160;damages&#160;or&#160;damages&#160;to&#160;neighboring&#160;properties&#160;if&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;causes&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:906px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">any&#160;such&#160;damage.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:928px;left:88px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2511"><b>11-7&#160;&#160;Dimensional Verification and&#160;Installation Compliance</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:928px;left:583px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2513"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:928px;left:587px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">–&#160;If&#160;applicable<b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:950px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:950px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">(A)&#160;&#160;The&#160;&#160;Second&#160;&#160;Party&#160;&#160;shall&#160;&#160;appoint&#160;&#160;a&#160;&#160;specialist&#160;&#160;before&#160;&#160;starting&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;installation&#160;&#160;of&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:972px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">dimensions,&#160;whose&#160;task&#160;is&#160;to&#160;inspect&#160;the&#160;dimensions&#160;according&#160;to&#160;the&#160;plans&#160;and&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:994px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">specifications&#160;and&#160;according&#160;to&#160;the&#160;original&#160;points,&#160;straights&#160;and&#160;reference&#160;clauses&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1016px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2512">indicated&#160;in&#160;the&#160;Contract,&#160;which&#160;was&#160;provided&#160;to&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;&#160;by&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1038px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2516">,&#160;as&#160;well&#160;as&#160;preparing&#160;a&#160;report&#160;in&#160;this&#160;regard,&#160;provided&#160;that&#160;a&#160;copy&#160;of&#160;it&#160;is&#160;delivered&#160;to&#160;<br/>the representative of&#160;the First&#160;Party&#160;.&#160;</p>
</div>
