<p style="position:absolute;top:1210px;left:856px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft267">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1224px;left:627px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft268">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:46px;left:293px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2610"><b>General Ts &amp;&#160;Cs&#160;Contract</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:46px;left:278px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2610"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:115px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:115px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">(B)&#160;The&#160;specialist&#160;must&#160;include&#160;in&#160;his&#160;report&#160;plans&#160;for&#160;all&#160;locations&#160;and&#160;points&#160;of&#160;facilities&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:136px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">and&#160;&#160;services,&#160;&#160;including,&#160;&#160;but&#160;&#160;not&#160;&#160;limited&#160;&#160;to,&#160;&#160;communications,&#160;&#160;sewage,&#160;&#160;water,&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:158px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">electricity,&#160;energy, transportation,&#160;firefighting&#160;units,&#160;and&#160;others.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:180px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:180px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">(C)&#160;The&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;is&#160;responsible&#160;for&#160;the&#160;Accuracy&#160;of&#160;fixing&#160;the&#160;coordinates&#160;of&#160;all&#160;parts&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:202px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">of&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;Works,&#160;&#160;and&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;Second&#160;&#160;Party&#160;&#160;must&#160;&#160;make&#160;&#160;every&#160;&#160;effort&#160;&#160;to&#160;&#160;investigate&#160;&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:224px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">Accuracy&#160;of&#160;the&#160;reference&#160;points&#160;and&#160;items&#160;before&#160;using&#160;them.&#160;If&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:246px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">delays&#160;the&#160;implementation&#160;of&#160;the&#160;Works&#160;due&#160;to&#160;false&#160;information&#160;in&#160;the&#160;reference&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:268px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">points&#160;&#160;and&#160;&#160;items&#160;&#160;provided&#160;&#160;by&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;First&#160;&#160;Party,&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;Second&#160;&#160;Party&#160;&#160;must&#160;&#160;send&#160;&#160;a&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:290px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">notification&#160;to&#160;the&#160;representative&#160;of&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;within&#160;a&#160;period&#160;of&#160;five&#160;(5)&#160;days&#160;to&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:312px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">enable the First&#160;Party&#160;to&#160;take&#160;the necessary&#160;corrective measures.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:334px;left:88px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2612"><b>11-8&#160;&#160;Site&#160;offices&#160;and&#160;storage&#160;areas&#160;</b>–&#160;If&#160;applicable<b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:356px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:356px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">(A)&#160;The&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;is&#160;committed&#160;to&#160;establishing&#160;temporary&#160;offices&#160;and&#160;storage&#160;places&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:378px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">within&#160;the&#160;boundaries&#160;of&#160;the&#160;site&#160;delivered&#160;to&#160;it&#160;according&#160;to&#160;the&#160;site&#160;handover&#160;report.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:400px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:400px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">(B)&#160;If&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;requests&#160;any&#160;additional&#160;spaces&#160;for&#160;mobilization,&#160;offices,&#160;storage&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:422px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">places,&#160;or&#160;any&#160;purposes&#160;related&#160;to&#160;the&#160;implementation&#160;of&#160;the&#160;Contract,&#160;and&#160;those&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:444px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">required&#160;spaces&#160;are&#160;outside&#160;the&#160;boundaries&#160;of&#160;the&#160;site&#160;delivered&#160;to&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party,&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:466px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">and&#160;if&#160;those&#160;spaces&#160;are&#160;available&#160;and&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;agrees&#160;to&#160;allocate&#160;them&#160;to&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:488px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">Second&#160;Party,&#160;the First&#160;Party&#160;has&#160;the right&#160;to&#160;demand&#160;that&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;pays&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:510px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">financial&#160;&#160;compensation&#160;&#160;for&#160;&#160;those&#160;&#160;spaces,&#160;&#160;facilities&#160;&#160;or&#160;&#160;utilities,&#160;&#160;or&#160;&#160;deducting&#160;&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:532px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">financial&#160;compensation&#160;for&#160;those&#160;spaces,&#160;facilities&#160;or&#160;utilities&#160;from&#160;the&#160;invoices&#160;of&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:554px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">the Second&#160;Party.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:576px;left:96px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2612"><b>12&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:576px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2612"><b>Declarations&#160;and&#160;pledges&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:598px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2612"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:598px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">The&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;acknowledges&#160;and&#160;undertakes&#160;to&#160;the First&#160;Party&#160;as&#160;follows:<b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:629px;left:88px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2612"><b>12-1&#160;&#160;Eligibility&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:650px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2612"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:650px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">(A)&#160;The&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;is legally&#160;established in&#160;accordance with&#160;the&#160;regulations of&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:673px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">state of&#160;incorporation.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:695px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2612"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:695px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">(B)&#160;All&#160;internal&#160;approvals&#160;were obtained&#160;from&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;to&#160;conclude and&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:717px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">implement&#160;this&#160;Contract&#160;and&#160;that&#160;this&#160;Contract&#160;is&#160;binding&#160;and&#160;enforceable.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:738px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2612"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:738px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">(C)&#160;All&#160;approvals,&#160;permits and&#160;licenses&#160;have been&#160;obtained from&#160;the concerned&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:760px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">authorities&#160;or&#160;third&#160;parties&#160;that&#160;should&#160;be obtained in&#160;connection&#160;with&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:782px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">conclusion&#160;and&#160;implementation&#160;of&#160;the Contract, and&#160;that&#160;all&#160;approvals,&#160;permits&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:804px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">and&#160;licenses&#160;are valid&#160;as&#160;on&#160;the date of&#160;this&#160;Contract&#160;and&#160;until&#160;its expiry.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:826px;left:88px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2612"><b>12-2&#160;&#160;Judicial&#160;disputes&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:848px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2612"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:848px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">(A)&#160;There is&#160;no&#160;dispute,&#160;case,&#160;investigation, arbitration&#160;or&#160;other&#160;existing&#160;or&#160;potential&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:870px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">proceeding&#160;that&#160;would&#160;adversely affect&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;’s ability&#160;to&#160;perform&#160;its&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:892px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">obligations under&#160;this&#160;Contract.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:914px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:914px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2611">(B)&#160;There&#160;are no&#160;court&#160;rulings,&#160;decisions,&#160;or&#160;similar&#160;orders from&#160;any&#160;competent&#160;</p>
