<p style="position:absolute;top:46px;left:278px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2810"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:115px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:115px;left:145px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;&#160;1.&#160;Poor&#160;performance&#160;in&#160;carrying&#160;out&#160;the work according&#160;to&#160;the criteria&#160;set out&#160;in&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:136px;left:181px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">appendix&#160;(7)&#160;Technical&#160;Specifications and&#160;Criteria&#160;for&#160;Evaluating&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:158px;left:181px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">Implementation&#160;of&#160;Works.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:180px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:180px;left:145px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;&#160;2.&#160;Any&#160;default, omission&#160;or&#160;misconduct&#160;by&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;or&#160;its&#160;representatives&#160;in&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:202px;left:181px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">connection&#160;with&#160;this&#160;Contract.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:224px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:224px;left:145px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;&#160;3.&#160;Any&#160;damages&#160;resulting&#160;from&#160;personal&#160;accidents&#160;or&#160;death&#160;to&#160;any&#160;of&#160;the employees&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:246px;left:181px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">of&#160;the Second&#160;Party,&#160;their&#160;Subcontractor,&#160;their&#160;representatives&#160;or&#160;any&#160;other&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:268px;left:181px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">person&#160;as&#160;a&#160;result&#160;of&#160;carrying&#160;out&#160;the work.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:290px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:290px;left:145px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;&#160;4.&#160;Any&#160;damages&#160;or&#160;losses&#160;resulting&#160;from&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;'s non-compliance with&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:312px;left:181px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">the provisions of&#160;appendix&#160;(10)&#160;Occupational&#160;Safety&#160;and&#160;Health&#160;Requirements.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:334px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:334px;left:145px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;&#160;5.&#160;Any&#160;breach&#160;of&#160;the applicable law.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:356px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:356px;left:145px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;&#160;6.&#160;Any&#160;violation&#160;of&#160;the pledges&#160;and/or&#160;representations stipulated in&#160;Clause (12)&#160;of&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:378px;left:181px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">the general&#160;terms&#160;and&#160;conditions of&#160;this&#160;Contract.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:400px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:400px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">(D)&#160;The&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;shall&#160;be&#160;liable&#160;to&#160;any&#160;third&#160;party&#160;who&#160;suffers&#160;damage&#160;as&#160;a&#160;result&#160;of&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:422px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">the error&#160;or&#160;omission&#160;of&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;in&#160;its implementation&#160;of&#160;the Contract.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:446px;left:96px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2812"><b>14&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:446px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2812"><b>Penalties&#160;and&#160;Deductions&#160;&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:468px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:468px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:490px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2812"><b>(A)&#160;Delay&#160;Penalty&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:511px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2814">If&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;delays&#160;in&#160;delivering&#160;or&#160;handing&#160;over&#160;the&#160;Works&#160;as&#160;per&#160;the&#160;contractual&#160;<br/>dates,&#160;the&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;may&#160;impose&#160;a&#160;delay&#160;penalty&#160;without&#160;prior&#160;notice.&#160;The&#160;penalty&#160;is&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:556px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2815">calculated&#160;based&#160;on&#160;the&#160;average&#160;daily&#160;cost&#160;of&#160;the&#160;project,&#160;determined&#160;by&#160;dividing&#160;the&#160;<br/>total&#160;Contract&#160;value&#160;by&#160;its duration.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:600px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:621px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">A&#160;special&#160;delay&#160;penalty&#160;of&#160;1%&#160;of&#160;the&#160;total&#160;Contract&#160;value&#160;per&#160;week&#160;of&#160;delay&#160;shall&#160;apply,&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:643px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">increasing&#160;by&#160;an&#160;additional&#160;1%&#160;for&#160;each&#160;subsequent&#160;week&#160;of&#160;delay.&#160;The&#160;total&#160;penalty&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:665px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">shall&#160;not&#160;exceed 10%&#160;of&#160;the total&#160;Contract&#160;value.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:687px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:709px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">Delay&#160;penalties&#160;apply&#160;if&#160;the Second&#160;Party&#160;fails&#160;to:&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:731px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:753px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">Deliver&#160;the Works&#160;in&#160;full&#160;within the total&#160;Contract&#160;duration.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:775px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">Meet&#160;basic&#160;milestone deadlines&#160;as&#160;specified&#160;in&#160;the Contract&#160;Data.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:797px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2814">The&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;has&#160;the&#160;right&#160;to&#160;deduct&#160;any&#160;applicable&#160;penalties&#160;from&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party’s&#160;<br/>entitlements under&#160;this&#160;Contract. The imposition&#160;of&#160;delay&#160;penalties&#160;does&#160;not&#160;affect&#160;the&#160;<br/>First&#160;Party’s&#160;right&#160;to&#160;claim&#160;further&#160;compensation&#160;as&#160;stipulated in&#160;this&#160;Contract.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:863px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:885px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2812"><b>(B)&#160;Deductions&#160;for Non-Performance&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:907px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">In&#160;addition&#160;to&#160;delay&#160;penalties,&#160;if&#160;the&#160;Second&#160;Party&#160;fails&#160;to&#160;perform&#160;any&#160;contractual&#160;Works&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:929px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">or&#160;&#160;does&#160;&#160;not&#160;&#160;provide&#160;&#160;the&#160;&#160;required&#160;&#160;number&#160;&#160;of&#160;&#160;basic&#160;&#160;or&#160;&#160;alternative&#160;&#160;manpower,&#160;&#160;the&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:951px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">corresponding&#160;amounts&#160;will not&#160;be payable.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:973px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:995px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">The&#160;First&#160;Party&#160;may&#160;deduct&#160;the&#160;value&#160;of&#160;missing&#160;or&#160;unperformed&#160;items&#160;and&#160;wages&#160;for&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1017px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2811">absent&#160;manpower&#160;from&#160;the&#160;allocated&#160;payments.&#160;This&#160;deduction&#160;is&#160;not&#160;subject&#160;to&#160;a&#160;10%&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:1039px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft2815">cap&#160;and&#160;may&#160;exceed that&#160;percentage.&#160;<br/>&#160;</p>
