<p style="position:absolute;top:422px;left:96px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft3412"><b>21&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:422px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft3412"><b>Intellectual&#160;property&#160;rights&#160;and&#160;protection&#160;</b></p>
