<p style="position:absolute;top:46px;left:293px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4510"><b>General Ts &amp;&#160;Cs&#160;Contract</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:46px;left:278px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4510"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:115px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4511">issued&#160;in&#160;the&#160;future&#160;in&#160;the&#160;Kingdom&#160;of&#160;Saudi&#160;Arabia.&#160;DACO,&#160;its&#160;subsidiaries,&#160;and&#160;the&#160;NCA&#160;also&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:136px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4511">have&#160;the&#160;right&#160;to&#160;conduct&#160;a&#160;compliance&#160;check&#160;to&#160;ensure&#160;the&#160;second&#160;party’s&#160;compliance&#160;with&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:158px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4511">cybersecurity.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:180px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4512"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:180px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4511">(7)&#160;The cybersecurity&#160;requirements for&#160;contracts&#160;and&#160;agreements with&#160;IT outsourcing.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:202px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4512"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:202px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4512"><b>(D) Architecture&#160;Requirements&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:224px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4512"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:224px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4511">(1)&#160;The&#160;Solution&#160;shall&#160;have&#160;a&#160;privacy&#160;module&#160;that&#160;includes&#160;the&#160;regulations,&#160;standards,&#160;and&#160;laws&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:246px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4511">around&#160;the platform.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:268px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4512"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:268px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4511">(2)&#160;The Solution&#160;shall&#160;have a&#160;Disaster&#160;Recovery&#160;(DR)&#160;dedicated instance.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:290px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4512"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:290px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4511">(3)&#160;The Solution&#160;shall&#160;provide&#160;capability&#160;for&#160;backup&#160;configurations.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:312px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4512"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:312px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4511">(4)&#160;The Solution&#160;shall&#160;support&#160;high&#160;availability.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:334px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4512"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:334px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4511">(5)&#160;The Solution&#160;shall&#160;support&#160;whole disk encryption&#160;with&#160;strong&#160;encryption&#160;algorithm.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:356px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4512"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:356px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4512"><b>(E)</b>&#160;<b>Privacy&#160;Requirements</b>&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:378px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4512"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:378px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4511">(1)&#160;&#160;The&#160;&#160;Solution&#160;&#160;shall&#160;&#160;have&#160;&#160;encryption&#160;&#160;standard,&#160;&#160;algorithm,&#160;&#160;and&#160;&#160;key&#160;&#160;lengths,&#160;&#160;for&#160;&#160;both&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:400px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4511">symmetric&#160;and&#160;asymmetric&#160;encryption,&#160;compatible&#160;with&#160;the&#160;different&#160;components.&#160;Refer&#160;to&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:422px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4511">IS-GI-022&#160;Cryptography&#160;General&#160;Instructions.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:444px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4512"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:444px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4511">(2)&#160;The Solution&#160;shall&#160;support&#160;classification&#160;with&#160;data&#160;classification&#160;tools if&#160;applicable.&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:466px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4512"><b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:466px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4511">(3)&#160;The&#160;Solution&#160;shall&#160;support&#160;the&#160;Access&#160;to&#160;system&#160;to&#160;be&#160;supported&#160;through&#160;security&#160;channels&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:488px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4511">only&#160;(e.g.&#160;HTTPS,&#160;SSH etc.).&#160;</p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:528px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4512"><b>&#160;</b></p>
