<p style="position:absolute;top:568px;left:170px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4511">Applicable Controls and&#160;Guidelines&#160;-&#160;National&#160;Cybersecurity&#160;Authority&#160;(nca.gov.sa)<b>&#160;</b></p>
<p style="position:absolute;top:594px;left:143px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft4511">▪</p>
